imdb.plot outline: The web series HOGWASH blends comedy and documentary to take viewers on a comic adventure through Oubliette, Louisiana, a town populated by a diverse array of obsessives and romantics all driven by improbable dreams, fiery cravings, and criminal instincts. Add it all up and you've got a chicken-scratch recipe for a small-town mystery whose center is everywhere and circumference nowhere.
